18:07.940 --> 18:09.694
- Get your hands off him!
- Get back.

18:09.781 --> 18:12.454
Come on, how could this possibly
end well for any of us?

18:12.838 --> 18:15.458
Look.
They got cameras.

18:18.123 --> 18:19.908
Fuck the police!

18:19.995 --> 18:21.996
Fuck the police!
