18:41.420 --> 18:43.264
But your students
are clearly angry.

18:43.351 --> 18:45.295
- They're protesting.
- Come on. Let's go.

18:45.382 --> 18:47.256
Look, of course
we'll have conversations

18:47.343 --> 18:49.074
about what led
to today's events,

18:49.161 --> 18:50.434
but these are teenagers.

18:50.521 --> 18:51.850
They're acting out.

18:52.086 --> 18:53.647
You're a new
principal, right?

18:53.734 --> 18:56.911
Is this protest a referendum
on how you're running things?

18:56.998 --> 18:58.311
