something?

27:12.243 --> 27:14.728
Is it true
you failed your own kid?

27:15.998 --> 27:17.229
No.

27:17.516 --> 27:20.181
He plagiarized.
He failed himself.

27:20.346 --> 27:22.275
What was I
supposed to do?

27:23.040 --> 27:24.572
Let it go?

27:25.774 --> 27:27.282
